com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model

Class Config

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model.Config
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Config
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    An abstract representation of configuration which Device must be updated with. It's simply a container of device's settings that can be configured.

    We can obtain configs via KontaktCloud.

    To create new instance of this class, please use Config.Builder.
